-- Westerwelle Wants European Growth Agenda, Handelsblatt Reports
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-01-25T06:34:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-25/westerwelle-wants-european-growth-agenda-handelsblatt-reports.html
The European Union needs an agenda
for growth and competitiveness to help overcome the region’s
debt crisis, German Foreign Minister  Guido Westerwelle  writes in
today’s  Handelsblatt .  Europe  is on a good path to restore confidence among people
and markets, Westerwelle added in his commentary.  To contact the reporter on this story:
